			title: "Home Base"
			icon: "minecraft:white_bed"
			subtitle: "Build something worth coming back to"
			description: [
				"§6Chapter 4§f is about the other side of Arcane Frontiers —"
				"§fnot progression and gates, but the home you build around that progression."
				""
				"§eThis chapter covers:§r"
				"§7• §e4.1 Building & Decoration§7 — CopyCats+, Supplementaries,"
				"§7  Decorative Blocks, Framed Blocks — tools to make any structure beautiful."
				"§7• §e4.2 Farming & Food§7 — Farmer's Delight, Straw Golem,"
				"§7  Cooking for Blockheads — sustainable food that buffs the whole family."
				"§7• §e4.3 Central Kitchen§7 — Create + Farmer's Delight automation."
				"§7  §e★ quests§7 require Ch 2 progress (Mechanical Arm, Deployer)."
				"§7• §e4.4 Home & Finishing§7 — trophy room, wall maps, The Chef's Edge."
				""
				"§eNo locked gates:§r"
				"§7• This chapter runs in parallel from the start."
				"§7• You can finish 4.1 and 4.2 without any magic or tech progress."
				"§7• The §e★ integration quests§7 in 4.3 need Ch 2 machines."
				"§7• The §e4.4 Chef's Edge§7 quest needs Ch 2.7 (Tetra Workbench)."
				""
				"§eStarting this quest:§r"
				"§7• Pick a build site for your main base."
				"§7• Place a §eBed§7, sleep through the night to set spawn."
				"§7• You're now anchored. Everything you build here is home."
				""
				"§a► Sleep in a bed. Mark done when you wake up with spawn set."
			]
			dependencies: []
		}

		{
