			icon: "supplementaries:sign_post"
			description: [
				"§6Supplementaries§f is the pack's primary decorative utility mod."
				"§fIt adds dozens of functional-decorative blocks that fill the gaps"
				"§fvanilla never addresses."
				""
				"§eHighlight items:§r"
				"§7• §eSign Post§7 — directional post with up to 4 wooden signs,"
				"§7  each pointing in a different direction. Perfect for colony roads,"
				"§7  cave systems, and path junctions."
				"§7  §eCrafting:§7 §e2 Sticks§7 + §e1 Oak Log§7 (vertical)."
				"§7• §eJar§7 — decorative glass jar that displays any item inside."
				"§7  Perfect for a pantry display above your kitchen."
				"§7• §eBookshelf§7 — displays books on the shelf visually."
				"§7• §eNotice Board§7 — wall-mounted sign with a larger text area."
				"§7  Great for colony announcements."
				"§7• §ePedestal§7 — spinning item display stand."
				"§7  Ideal for trophy room items — boss heads, rare drops."
				"§7• §eFlagpole§7 — animated banner on a pole, stackable height."
				"§7• §eRope§7 — hangable rope that you can climb. Finally."
				"§7• §eLantern§7 variants — wall, hanging, and floor variants."
				"§7• §eFirefly§7 jars — decorative ambient lighting, catch fireflies at night."
				""
				"§a► Craft a Sign Post and hold it."
			]
			dependencies: ["000E0001"]
