			title: "First Farm"
			icon: "minecraft:farmland"
			description: [
				"§6Farming§f in Arcane Frontiers is dramatically expanded over vanilla"
				"§fby §6Farmer's Delight§f and its companion mods."
				"§fYour first farm is the foundation of the family food supply."
				""
				"§eSetting up a farm:§r"
				"§71. §eTill Dirt§7 or §eGrass§7 with a §eHoe§7 → Farmland."
				"§72. §eWater§7 must be within 4 blocks — farmland dries otherwise."
				"§73. §ePlant seeds§7 — right-click farmland with seed items."
				"§7   A 4×4 = 16-block farm is the minimum for this quest."
				""
				"§eFarmer's Delight crops (not in vanilla):§r"
				"§7• §eCabbage§7 — grows in cold biomes. Source: wander or dungeon chests."
				"§7• §eTomato§7 — warm biome, vines up a trellis. Very productive."
				"§7• §eOnion§7 — temperate biome, fast-growing."
				"§7• §eRice§7 — grows on flooded farmland (water on top)."
				"§7• §eBeet§7 — cold, generates in village farms."
				""
				"§eGet Farmer's Delight seeds:§r"
				"§7• §eVillage farms§7 contain FD crops — harvest and replant."
				"§7• §eWandering Traders§7 sometimes sell FD seed packets."
				"§7• §eDungeon chests§7 (D&T tavern especially) often contain FD seeds."
				"§7• §eYour Cabbage Seeds reward§7 — plant all 8 to start your Cabbage row."
				""
				"§aStraw Golem tip (next quest):§r"
				"§7• Build the farm first, then place the Straw Golem inside."
				"§7• It only harvests what it can reach from its placement block."
				""
				"§a► Till and plant 16+ crop blocks. Mark done when your first farm is planted."
			]
			dependencies: ["000E0001"]
		}

