			title: "Farmer's Delight"
			icon: "farmersdelight:skillet"
			description: [
				"§6Farmer's Delight§f is the pack's primary food expansion mod."
				"§fIt adds §e30+ new crops§f, §e50+ recipes§f, and an entirely new"
				"§fcooking workflow using cutting boards, skillets, and cooking pots."
				""
				"§eThe Skillet:§r"
				"§7• §eCrafting:§7 §e5 Iron Ingots§7 in a frying pan shape"
				"§7  (left arm + handle + flat base)."
				"§7• Place over a heat source (§eCampfire§7, §eLit Furnace§7, or §eMagma Block§7)."
				"§7• Right-click to place items in the skillet, wait for cooking."
				"§7• Used for: §eSunnyside Egg§7, §eSmoked Ham§7, §eRoasted Mutton§7, and more."
				""
				"§eSaturation vs. hunger:§r"
				"§7• Vanilla food fills §ehunger bars§7 (the bar you can see)."
				"§7• FD meals add §esaturation§7 — hidden buffer that slows hunger drain."
				"§7• A §eRoast Chicken dinner§7 (Cooking Pot) gives 8 hunger + §e14 saturation§7"
				"§7  vs. Steak's 8 hunger + §e12 saturation§7."
				"§7• With FD meals, you §eeat far less often§7. Huge combat advantage."
				""
				"§eWhy two Skillets?§r"
				"§7• The reward skillet is a §esecond one§7 — keep one at the base,"
				"§7  carry one in your backpack. Skillet cooking works anywhere"
				"§7  there's a campfire."
				""
				"§a► Craft a Skillet and hold it in your hand."
			]
			dependencies: ["000E0006"]
		}

