				"§fmakes §emulti-ingredient meals§f with stacked saturation bonuses."
				""
				"§eCrafting:§r"
				"§7• §e7 Iron Ingots§7 in a pot shape (U-shape with handles)."
				"§7• Requires a heat source beneath (Campfire, Magma, Lit Furnace)."
				""
				"§eUsing it:§r"
				"§7• Right-click to open the cooking interface."
				"§7• Place §eup to 6 ingredients§7 in the input slots."
				"§7• Insert a §eBowl or Bottle§7 to receive the meal."
				"§7• Progress bar fills as ingredients are processed over the heat source."
				""
				"§eTop Cooking Pot recipes:§r"
				"§7• §eVegetable Soup§7 — Carrot + Potato + Cabbage + Bowl. Huge saturation."
				"§7• §eRoast Chicken§7 — Raw Chicken + Potato + Onion + Bottle."
				"§7  Serves 4 bowls at once."
				"§7• §eMutton Stew§7 — Raw Mutton + Carrot + Onion + Potato + Bowl."
				"§7• §eBone Broth§7 — Bone + Water Bottle. Base ingredient for advanced soups."
				"§7• §eSeasoned Salmon§7 — Raw Salmon + Carrot + Onion + Bottle."
				""
				"§eAutomation (Ch 4.3):§r"
				"§7• The §eCentral Kitchen§7 quests automate the Cooking Pot with Create."
				"§7• A §eMechanical Arm§7 feeds ingredients → Pot → collects meals."
				""
				"§a► Craft and hold a Cooking Pot. (16 Tomato Seeds reward: plant them!)"
