			description: [
				"§6The Straw Golem§f auto-harvests mature crops and replants them."
				"§fPlace one in your farm and it becomes self-sustaining —"
				"§fno more manual harvesting."
				""
				"§eCrafting:§r"
				"§7• §e1 Carved Pumpkin§7 + §e1 Hay Bale§7 (vertical, shapeless)."
				"§7• The Carved Pumpkin becomes the golem's head."
